---
id: verify_number
sidebar_label: Verify Number
title: Verify Number
---
Instead of using GINAR verification tool, PoD API supports to get JSON Data by sessionId
## PoD
* API URL:
> https://api.ginar.io/rng/pod/ **{sessionId}**
* Method: ``GET``
* Parameters:
	* **sessionKey**: a valid session key
		* _type_: **string** (required)
		* _constraint_: 256-bit hex-string
* Return:  a JSON string including result and Eligible Contributors from GINAR system

* Sample request: 
``` 
https://api.ginar.io/rng/pod/1750154f00c7fab4d68d4f1318ea70aaa24655d0283957c6c20e98c1867f270a
```
